                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In domo <persName>Ferrariorum</persName>. <persName>Sibilia</persName> uxor
                            <persName>Ercarii Ferrarii</persName>, presente eius viro, et
                            <persName>Beatris </persName>mater <persName>Roberti Ferrarii</persName>
                        et <persName>Matelda</persName> eius uxor, presente eius viro et
                        consenciente vendicionibus de <rs key="#Areas #Rivers">terra de Riva</rs> et
                        de <rs key="#Areas #Rivers">terra de ultra Trebia</rs> atque refutacionibus
                        quas ipsi Ercarius et Robertus fecerunt domino <persName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/16">Gandulfo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/53"
                            key="#Areas #Rivers">S. Sisti</orgName>. <rs key="#Witness">Testes</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness">Albericus Brachiumforte</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness">Guido Buxus</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                            >Bertolotus Bonaminus</persName> et <persName key="#Witness">Obertus
                            Ferrarius</persName>
                        <persName key="#Notary">Petrus Lachetta</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>.</ab>
